node.text: #ad Sharing my favorite Charlotte hot spots as well as my MIRACLE product for protecting your skin against daily pollution – the @neutrogena Hydro Boost City Shield Water Gel SPF 25! The entire City Shield line is so easy to incorporate into your daily routine, and they're small enough to fit in your handbag. And if you live in Charlotte, be sure to check out @notjustcoffee and @fahrenheitclt, two of my favorite spots in the city! #HydroBoostCityShield

node.title: My Favorite Charlotte Spots with Neutrogena

node.text: Thank you to @ardenfilmco for capturing such a special day in our lives 💕 We’re so incredibly happy we went with them to film our big day! There were so many small, special moments throughout the day that we both had forgotten about and @ardenfilmco was able to capture them for us. And of course, happy Valentine’s Day to my hubby @cmdorsch on our first Valentine’s Day as a married couple! I love you so much!!! Please let me know if you have any questions guys & I’ll answer them in the comments 💗 #ardenclips #ardenfilmco #wedding #weddingvideo #weddingvideographer #valentinesday #valentinesday2018

node.text: Helloooo from Iceland! My brother and I are having a blast exploring - we’ve been driving from coast to coast to explore all that Iceland has to offer. We hiked a glacier, visited diamond beach, climbed to the top of a waterfall, walked around a massive volcano crater, & more. Thank you so much @noken for this wonderful experience! 💗 I’ll be sharing a blog post with all the information if you’re interested! #igtv #iceland #igtvcommunity #glacier #noken #travel #travelguide #vlog #travelvideo #video

node.text: When you’re a mom, self-care is even more important - by taking care of myself I have so much more to offer my daughter than I do when I am running on empty. That’s why I use @athenaclub products - luxurious shower products and a super smooth shave make me feel more like myself even on stressful days. And seeing these pretty pink products in my shower puts a smile on my face! Linking the products here: http://liketk.it/3mcsH #athenaclub #momlife #selfcare # ad

node.text: My cuties 👶🏼🐶 Kennedy is such a happy baby! She honestly smiles like this all day long 🥺 but to be honest, even though *she* is so happy, *I* sometimes feel guilty for not feeling as happy as I think I should feel. I’ve really been struggling with anxiety as a new mom… I worry about everything pertaining to Kennedy, all the time, big and small things, realistic things and unrealistic things. I have trouble living in the moment and truly enjoying my baby because of it. From some of the DMs you’ve sent, it sounds like a lot of you feel or have felt the same. If you’ve been through this before, I’d love to know what helped you. 💗 #newmom #momandbaby #momlife
